Egg group - FIELD / GRASS

This creature can whip its vine-like tail at 50mph to quickly stun its prey. It thoroughly enjoys basking in the sun.
A cat composed of luscious leaf petals. Each Fall the petals fall out and regrow in the Spring.
It has such a high flow rate of Potassium and Sodium ions that it can conduct electricity.
